# Build precondition

Always build Kleis using `./scripts/build-kleis.sh`, never with raw `cargo build`.

The build script handles Z3 header detection, artifact cleanup, and installs
the binary to `~/bin/kleis` and `~/.cargo/bin/kleis` so the LSP extension and
MCP servers pick up the latest version.
